{"tid":875699,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港股弱勢連跌6個月 自1982年最長紀錄","createTime":"2018-10-25T05:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T05:27:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abb530e4904899792d74dcb74e4bdecf10820ff3","tid":875699,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181025/large/1540441798_5940.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181025%2Flarge%2F1540441798_5940.jpg&h=a533946e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恒指今早開市即大跌約2%，若收市維持2%或以上的跌幅，今年將出現13次跌超2%的情況，會追平2015年中國股災引發的大跌市，2017年全年只曾出現兩次。<br />\n<br />\n根據彭博報道，港股今年受多方外圍因素拖累下跌，美科技股大跌、A股暴瀉、貿易戰影響經濟前景、人民幣貶值等，恒指技術上早已落入熊市，10月份更跌了9.1%，勢創連續六個月下挫，這將是自1982年以來最長連跌紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181025/58833722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58833722&d=f6XO8Y%2B%2BjjptGczM%2FaMCX5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=bc4dd6b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181025%2F58833722&h=83e24292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181025/58833722</a>"},{"pid":"be8ad41097bdbe49b08b500005a7d3b992479f8a","tid":875699,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"有種跌足 12 個月啦<br />\n<br />\n美國就最長升浪 港豬就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1deac290acd118b3f4763b4c17ca748b6c9456a","tid":875699,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be8ad41097bdbe49b08b500005a7d3b992479f8a","tid":875699,"uid":29093,"like":2